Maybe there should be a version of FedoarID.create() like the following:
public static FedoraID create(String part, String... parts) {
    // enforce part not blank

    if (parts != null && parts.length > 0) {
        final var sb = new StringBuilder(part);
        Arrays.asList(parts).forEach(p -> {
            appendSlash(sb).append(p);
        });
    }

    // Check for trailing slash?
    // create FedoraID
}

private StringBuilder appendSlash(final StringBuilder sb) {
    if (sb.charAt(sb.count() - 1) != '/') {
        sb.append("/");
    }
    return sb;
}

