This partly depends on what you think about another suggestion, further down:
#1652 (comment)
But if we end up keeping fcr:metadata in the fullId, a call to resolveId(String... additions) would inspect the additions. If one of them was fcr:metadata, I believe we would want it to call return FedoraID.create(this.getResourceId(), addition);, otherwise we call return FedoraID.create(this.getFullId(), addition);

